<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='845270' id='t-845270'>as natural resources.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='847228' id='t-847228'>And so we stand at a crossroads.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='849466' id='t-849466'>An option is to go through that rethinking</span>
