<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='854438' id='t-854438'>to change how we do business.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='856992' id='t-856992'>The alternative is</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='859253' id='t-859253'>a world in which even a blade of grass</span>
